title: Cody Fern as Stan Vogel | American Horror Stories - Episode 6: "Feral" (HQ Clip)
author: AHS Crave
comment: AHAHA love the people online saying his Aussie accent is awful when he's actually from Australia and this is his normal voice 😂😂
This was my favorite episode thus far. I would love to see this plot expanded, they could do a sequel episode or even a whole season.
I love that this episode has a strong Australian feel, from Cody using his natural accent to the color palette of the cinematography. Got Wolf Creek vibes a bit
Cody Fern has a lovely Australian accent 💖
description: "Feral" is the sixth episode of Ryan Murphy & Brad Falchuk's "American Horror Stories," the official "AHS"/"American Horror Story" spin-off series, exclusive to FX on Hulu. Written & directed by Manny Coto, the episode stars Cody Fern as Stan Vogel, Aaron Tveit as Jay Gantz, Tiffany DuPont as Addy Gantz, Blake Shields (Bob Birch), and Colin Tandberg as Jacob Gantz. All rights belong to 20th Television, FX Productions, and Ryan Murphy Productions.
